WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:51.000 --> 01:51.880
I am telling you

01:52.520 --> 01:55.240
the secret I wanted to seal away forever.

01:56.720 --> 01:57.600
Can you…

02:02.400 --> 02:03.720
Can you believe

02:03.800 --> 02:05.320
that you are a great person?

02:08.720 --> 02:09.919
Seeing how much

02:10.840 --> 02:12.240
I like you,

02:13.920 --> 02:16.800
can you ignore what people say about you?

02:20.400 --> 02:22.640
Can you be with me forever?

02:27.720 --> 02:30.160
MAKE A LOT OF MONEY
AND HELP HIM PAY OFF HIS DEBTS

02:34.040 --> 02:34.920
Please?

02:39.680 --> 02:41.560
How do you fold this star?

02:43.400 --> 02:45.000
I can't fold it back after unfolding it.

02:46.320 --> 02:47.360
After unfolding it, I…

03:20.720 --> 03:21.640
These stars

03:22.520 --> 03:23.920
will be in my safekeeping.

03:29.000 --> 03:29.960
What should I do now?

03:30.920 --> 03:32.040
Counting it now,

03:32.600 --> 03:34.000
I've made you cry so many times.

03:36.320 --> 03:37.800
Yet you deny that you're a crybaby.

03:42.520 --> 03:43.360
Give me a hug.

04:00.040 --> 04:01.280
All right.

04:03.520 --> 04:04.640
I know it all now.

04:13.200 --> 04:15.200
Why did you suddenly tell me this?

04:16.839 --> 04:18.279
I just wanted you to know.

04:19.120 --> 04:19.959
But this time,

04:20.839 --> 04:22.280
I don't have that rumored girlfriend

04:22.360 --> 04:23.480
that your brother mentioned.

04:25.160 --> 04:27.280
I have an official girlfriend now.

04:31.400 --> 04:33.920
So did you come back to Yihe

04:35.040 --> 04:36.200
just to tell me this?

04:37.840 --> 04:39.200
It's because you said

04:40.160 --> 04:41.600
you were considering something.

04:42.680 --> 04:43.920
That's why…

04:46.080 --> 04:48.720
I was afraid that if I called you,
you would…

04:52.400 --> 04:54.520
I thought that
if I talked to you in person,

04:55.840 --> 04:58.560
it should be hard for you to bring it up.

04:59.680 --> 05:00.560
Bring what up?

05:07.080 --> 05:08.280
What were you thinking?

05:14.440 --> 05:16.960
If your parents hadn't disapproved,

05:17.040 --> 05:19.160
I would snatch you
to get our marriage certificate now.

05:21.840 --> 05:22.920
I'm serious.

05:23.440 --> 05:25.360
Why would you have to snatch me?

05:26.360 --> 05:28.080
I'm afraid you will run away.

05:30.440 --> 05:32.320
When I said I was considering something,

05:32.400 --> 05:35.000
it was whether I should stay with you
in Yihe for two years

05:35.080 --> 05:37.160
and go back with you after you graduate

05:37.240 --> 05:38.800
or if I should go to Nanwu first

05:38.880 --> 05:39.880
to get everything settled

05:39.960 --> 05:41.000
and wait for you to return.

05:41.920 --> 05:43.280
What were you thinking?

05:46.720 --> 05:47.720
Is that it?

05:54.920 --> 05:55.840
Actually,

05:56.440 --> 05:58.680
I could stay in Yihe too.

05:59.680 --> 06:01.040
We can talk about it.

06:01.920 --> 06:03.800
You don't always have to give in to me.

06:04.520 --> 06:06.160
I really don't want to stay here.

06:06.880 --> 06:08.880
Besides, who else would I give in to?

06:11.760 --> 06:12.880
Young lady,

06:12.960 --> 06:15.240
what you need to do is simple.

06:15.320 --> 06:17.280
Stay here and study hard.

06:17.360 --> 06:18.640
Don't worry about anything else.

06:19.520 --> 06:21.000
The most important thing

06:21.080 --> 06:23.400
is to spend more time with your boyfriend.

06:23.920 --> 06:24.760
Understand?

06:29.920 --> 06:31.320
As for your parents,

06:32.920 --> 06:34.000
don't worry about it.

06:34.560 --> 06:37.400
I'll find time to talk to them.

06:42.440 --> 06:43.280
Smile.

06:49.080 --> 06:50.160
Give me a smile.

07:11.800 --> 07:14.400
CHAPTER 24, SET OFF

07:14.480 --> 07:16.560
SO NEAR AND YET SO FAR

07:34.160 --> 07:36.520
There is someone

07:36.600 --> 07:37.880
that I really like.

07:38.640 --> 07:39.480
But

07:40.600 --> 07:42.240
he just doesn't like me.

07:44.520 --> 07:46.280
But I will grow up.

07:46.360 --> 07:48.440
Then let's wait until you grow up.

07:48.520 --> 07:49.440
But when I grow up,

07:49.520 --> 07:51.160
he'll fall for someone else.

07:54.000 --> 07:55.080
That's fine.

07:55.800 --> 07:57.760
Sang Zhi, when you grow up,

07:58.560 --> 08:00.400
you will meet someone better.

08:34.000 --> 08:35.320
Why have you been drinking?

08:39.159 --> 08:40.320
What's wrong?

08:43.520 --> 08:45.120
I'll bring you some hot water.

08:51.080 --> 08:52.440
Why did you get up?

08:59.080 --> 09:00.840
Are you in a bad mood?

09:02.880 --> 09:03.800
I think

09:08.120 --> 09:09.360
that I've treated you badly.

09:16.720 --> 09:18.520
When did you treat me badly?

09:29.000 --> 09:31.360
Is it because of what I said to you

09:31.440 --> 09:32.840
at the airport today?

09:35.680 --> 09:36.560
I told you that

09:36.640 --> 09:38.360
because I just wanted you to know.

09:39.440 --> 09:40.800
You didn't know it before.

09:40.880 --> 09:42.440
That's why I wanted to tell you.

09:42.920 --> 09:44.320
But I didn't want you to feel…

09:51.720 --> 09:53.160
You treat me very well.

09:54.120 --> 09:55.840
Be it in the past or the present,

09:57.200 --> 09:58.160
you treat me well.

09:59.680 --> 10:00.520
It's true.

10:00.600 --> 10:01.480
Sang Zhi.

10:05.520 --> 10:06.440
I love you.

10:16.280 --> 10:17.520
I'm sorry, Zhizhi.

10:19.600 --> 10:21.560
I said these words so late.

10:28.280 --> 10:29.640
Over the years,

10:32.760 --> 10:33.960
I know

10:35.280 --> 10:36.440
I've made you sad.

10:40.400 --> 10:42.120
It was your unwavering dedication

10:43.520 --> 10:46.080
that made me realize I'm not good enough.

10:48.400 --> 10:50.440
Whether it's my imperceptiveness

10:51.720 --> 10:53.400
or indecisiveness,

10:54.920 --> 10:56.240
I haven't been good enough.

11:01.800 --> 11:03.200
But for these shortcomings,

11:04.680 --> 11:06.840
I'll try my best to make it up to you

11:06.920 --> 11:08.200
every day that we are together.

11:10.320 --> 11:11.200
Zhizhi.

11:16.240 --> 11:17.600
I won't let you regret

11:17.680 --> 11:19.640
the choice you made.

11:24.480 --> 11:25.920
I love you, Sang Zhi.

12:46.400 --> 12:48.120
Sangsang, what are you drawing?

12:48.920 --> 12:51.160
I found my theme for the competition.

12:52.640 --> 12:53.640
What did I tell you?

12:53.720 --> 12:54.920
You can't force ideas to come.

12:55.000 --> 12:56.160
You need to clear your mind

12:56.240 --> 12:57.560
for inspiration to come.

12:58.800 --> 12:59.920
So what is your theme?

13:03.800 --> 13:04.880
Why are you being secretive?

13:16.400 --> 13:17.240
Come in.

13:20.000 --> 13:21.200
Siyun.

13:21.280 --> 13:23.200
Perfect timing. Come here quickly.

13:23.280 --> 13:24.440
Help me take a look.

13:25.040 --> 13:26.000
I have trouble deciding.

13:26.080 --> 13:27.480
Which one of these two is better?

13:28.600 --> 13:29.840
I think

13:30.520 --> 13:31.360
this one is the best.

13:32.560 --> 13:34.160
- What is this?
- Open it.

13:35.280 --> 13:37.080
You've been working late nights lately,

13:37.160 --> 13:38.280
so I bought you a gift.

13:40.720 --> 13:41.760
Restorative honey?

13:41.840 --> 13:42.840
Xiaoduan recommended it.

13:45.640 --> 13:46.680
He sure knows what to pick.

13:46.760 --> 13:48.280
This kid knows a lot of things.

13:48.360 --> 13:49.400
It smells quite nice.

13:51.240 --> 13:52.600
Come in.

13:56.360 --> 13:58.120
Actually, I wanted to talk

13:58.200 --> 14:00.120
to both of you about something today.

14:00.800 --> 14:02.000
What is it?

14:02.080 --> 14:03.160
I was thinking

14:03.240 --> 14:04.800
that after completing the upgrade

14:04.880 --> 14:06.360
of the Celestial Progression System,

14:07.440 --> 14:08.840
I might have to resign.

14:10.920 --> 14:12.160
Resign?

14:12.240 --> 14:13.920
Why do you suddenly want to resign?

14:15.520 --> 14:17.280
Is another company trying to poach you?

14:18.520 --> 14:19.440
No.

14:19.920 --> 14:21.640
I'm thinking of going back to Nanwu

14:21.720 --> 14:23.000
to start my own business.

14:23.560 --> 14:24.400
Nanwu?

14:25.600 --> 14:26.680
Is it for Sang Zhi?

14:28.760 --> 14:29.800
If I'm not mistaken,

14:29.880 --> 14:31.360
isn't she only a college sophomore?

14:31.920 --> 14:33.320
When she graduates in two years,

14:33.400 --> 14:35.480
you can still go back there with her.

14:37.520 --> 14:39.040
The Dream Games studio

14:39.120 --> 14:41.480
has a very promising next few years.

14:42.000 --> 14:43.920
Are you sure about leaving now?

14:46.000 --> 14:48.000
I have carefully considered it

14:48.080 --> 14:49.360
before telling you.

14:51.680 --> 14:53.640
Some things have happened recently.

14:54.240 --> 14:55.280
It made me realize

14:55.760 --> 14:57.160
I may not have been good enough

14:57.240 --> 14:58.640
to Sang Zhi.

14:58.720 --> 15:00.280
I haven't done enough for her either.

15:00.360 --> 15:01.920
No, Jiaxu, you're worrying too much.

15:02.000 --> 15:04.280
Siyun and I both think
that you treat her really well.

15:07.280 --> 15:08.600
Actually, the main reason

15:09.520 --> 15:10.760
is that her parents

15:10.840 --> 15:12.520
may have some concerns about me.

15:15.800 --> 15:18.280
Sang Zhi is also upset

15:18.880 --> 15:19.840
because of this.

15:21.320 --> 15:22.480
However,

15:22.560 --> 15:24.480
she turned around and comforted me.

15:25.520 --> 15:26.960
She was worried

15:27.040 --> 15:28.560
that this might hurt my self-esteem.

15:28.640 --> 15:30.080
In truth, I understand

15:30.160 --> 15:31.600
her parents' concerns.

15:33.160 --> 15:34.640
But I'm older than her.

15:35.280 --> 15:36.840
So I should be the one

15:36.920 --> 15:38.360
resolving these concerns.

15:39.560 --> 15:40.720
I just want to go

15:40.800 --> 15:42.440
to Nanwu as soon as possible.

15:42.520 --> 15:44.520
After I've settled everything,

15:45.120 --> 15:47.000
I'll give myself more time

15:47.080 --> 15:48.760
and chances to prove myself.

15:52.600 --> 15:53.800
He's all grown up now.

15:53.880 --> 15:56.160
A man should have
a sense of responsibility.

16:01.880 --> 16:04.360
Since you've already made up your mind,

16:04.920 --> 16:06.880
Li Xun and I can't stop you.

16:08.040 --> 16:09.120
We wish you all the best.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.320
Thank you.

16:12.400 --> 16:13.240
However,

16:13.320 --> 16:16.960
today's economy isn't easy

16:17.040 --> 16:18.040
for young entrepreneurs.

16:19.120 --> 16:20.360
Given your qualifications,

16:20.440 --> 16:22.200
there aren't many
reputable companies in Nanwu

16:22.280 --> 16:23.160
that can hire you.

16:23.240 --> 16:24.320
How about this?

16:25.000 --> 16:26.760
You can apply to our headquarters

16:26.840 --> 16:28.640
to open your own studio.

16:29.280 --> 16:31.520
They can provide some technical support

16:31.600 --> 16:32.920
and follow-up expansion,

16:33.000 --> 16:34.880
which would be relatively easier for you.

16:34.960 --> 16:35.920
Look at that.

16:36.000 --> 16:37.600
Siyun thinks of everything.

16:37.680 --> 16:39.160
Our company does have this policy.

16:39.240 --> 16:41.120
If you need it,
Siyun and I will put in a word.

16:42.840 --> 16:44.600
It would be great if that could happen.

16:45.120 --> 16:46.120
Thank you, Li Xun.

16:46.680 --> 16:48.040
Thank you, Siyun.

16:48.120 --> 16:49.080
You're welcome.

16:50.120 --> 16:53.040
If you create a successful game
in the future,

16:53.120 --> 16:54.360
I'll get to boast about it.

16:54.440 --> 16:56.080
I can say that I mentored this guy.

16:58.000 --> 17:00.120
You were still an intern

17:00.200 --> 17:01.800
when you first came.

17:01.880 --> 17:02.720
Look at you now.

17:03.320 --> 17:04.720
So many years have passed.

17:05.520 --> 17:07.040
Now that you're leaving,

17:07.119 --> 17:08.560
I'm actually quite reluctant.

17:11.400 --> 17:12.240
You can do it.

17:12.319 --> 17:14.240
- Good luck.
- LI Xun and I support you.

17:14.319 --> 17:15.560
- You can do it.
- I'll do my best.

17:34.480 --> 17:35.320
Hello?

17:36.560 --> 17:38.240
The patient's condition isn't optimistic.

17:38.320 --> 17:40.240
Cherish the time and talk to him.

17:40.880 --> 17:41.920
Thank you, doctor.

18:29.720 --> 18:31.880
It has been a long time
since I thought about the past.

18:34.280 --> 18:35.240
I didn't want to

18:36.720 --> 18:37.880
and I didn't dare to.

18:41.280 --> 18:42.280
But I think

18:43.520 --> 18:45.280
today should be the day that I face it.

18:47.640 --> 18:48.920
I should get some closure.

18:52.240 --> 18:54.040
It happened such a long time ago.

18:55.640 --> 18:56.960
Now that I think about it,

18:59.320 --> 19:01.200
you would have been released by now

19:03.160 --> 19:04.920
if you hadn't jumped.

19:09.160 --> 19:10.480
There are many things

19:12.040 --> 19:13.560
that I've never told you.

19:17.160 --> 19:19.120
I've finished paying off

19:20.840 --> 19:22.360
the compensation you owed

19:23.400 --> 19:24.680
and those debts of yours.

19:27.320 --> 19:28.200
My mom

19:31.920 --> 19:33.360
passed away several years ago.

19:38.280 --> 19:39.280
Because of you.

19:42.080 --> 19:43.480
Because we didn't have money.

19:52.840 --> 19:54.200
At that time,

19:55.400 --> 19:57.520
she knew she was sick

19:57.600 --> 19:58.600
from cancer.

20:00.880 --> 20:02.040
She refused to get treatment

20:02.120 --> 20:03.640
because she didn't want to spend money.

20:07.720 --> 20:09.440
When she finally went to the hospital,

20:11.160 --> 20:12.920
the doctor said
it was too late for treatment.

20:25.400 --> 20:28.120
I used to wish so badly
that you could see it all.

20:30.040 --> 20:31.520
I wished you would wake up,

20:32.640 --> 20:35.840
so you could see everything
that happened to us.

20:37.880 --> 20:40.480
I wanted to see you feel guilt and pain.

20:45.640 --> 20:47.640
I just wanted you to understand.

20:49.880 --> 20:51.040
If you hadn't

20:52.360 --> 20:53.600
run away

20:54.160 --> 20:55.920
and had chosen to face punishment,

20:57.920 --> 20:59.880
our lives would have been so different.

21:14.680 --> 21:16.080
But actually,

21:18.160 --> 21:19.400
I should thank you too.

21:21.920 --> 21:22.960
Because of you,

21:24.280 --> 21:25.560
I never dared to drink.

21:27.600 --> 21:28.840
It was also because of you

21:29.600 --> 21:31.200
that I learned what responsibility

21:31.280 --> 21:32.640
and taking on responsibility means.

21:35.080 --> 21:36.160
Now,

21:40.880 --> 21:42.480
I can say

21:42.560 --> 21:44.040
that I'm a decent person.

21:47.880 --> 21:49.480
At least I now have the ability

21:51.160 --> 21:52.920
to protect the people I love.

21:54.760 --> 21:56.640
I really wish you could see it.

22:05.840 --> 22:06.760
All right then.

22:09.800 --> 22:11.160
If you see Mom

22:13.120 --> 22:14.520
on the other side,

22:18.040 --> 22:19.640
sincerely apologize to her.

22:30.520 --> 22:31.480
Be at peace,

22:35.240 --> 22:36.200
Dad.

23:53.920 --> 23:54.880
Why are you here?

24:00.240 --> 24:01.480
What's with this expression?

24:02.880 --> 24:03.800
I knew

24:04.320 --> 24:05.840
this day would come eventually.

24:46.120 --> 24:47.440
I know.

24:48.720 --> 24:50.600
I know you're very sad.

24:51.800 --> 24:52.840
I know that.

24:56.280 --> 24:57.360
Okay, it's all right.

25:01.840 --> 25:03.840
Am I really getting old now?

25:09.440 --> 25:12.040
Why are my parents no longer here?

25:43.680 --> 25:47.200
GRACE UPON DESCENDANTS

25:47.280 --> 25:50.400
IN MEMORY OF BELOVED MOTHER,
XU RUOSHU

26:00.480 --> 26:02.680
Mom, you haven't met her yet.

26:04.920 --> 26:06.160
This is Sang Zhi.

26:07.160 --> 26:09.960
I've told you about her before.

26:11.400 --> 26:12.280
Now,

26:13.000 --> 26:14.440
she is my girlfriend.

26:20.800 --> 26:21.720
Mom.

26:22.320 --> 26:24.280
I might settle down in Nanwu later.

26:25.320 --> 26:26.400
But don't worry.

26:27.400 --> 26:29.760
I'll come and visit you every year.

26:31.240 --> 26:33.280
I came today mainly to tell you

26:34.480 --> 26:35.640
that Dad has also passed away.

26:37.640 --> 26:38.600
He passed away

26:40.520 --> 26:41.560
quite peacefully.

26:43.760 --> 26:45.120
Don't worry.

26:45.200 --> 26:46.680
I fulfilled his wish

26:46.760 --> 26:49.040
and found a serene place for him.

26:49.120 --> 26:50.040
I wonder

26:50.720 --> 26:52.680
if you two will meet over there.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.880
If you do…

27:14.360 --> 27:15.560
Never mind.

27:16.520 --> 27:18.920
As long as both of you
are happy and content.

27:51.760 --> 27:52.720
Hello, Mrs. Duan.

27:54.440 --> 27:55.720
I'm Sang Zhi.

27:59.040 --> 28:00.480
You don't have to worry.

28:01.680 --> 28:03.760
Duan Jiaxu is now

28:03.840 --> 28:06.360
a very kind and outstanding person.

28:08.520 --> 28:11.360
He treats people well

28:11.440 --> 28:12.600
and is very sincere.

28:13.080 --> 28:14.720
He excelled in his studies

28:14.800 --> 28:16.360
and performs well at work.

28:17.120 --> 28:18.280
To me,

28:19.440 --> 28:20.520
my parents,

28:21.080 --> 28:22.320
and everyone,

28:22.800 --> 28:24.920
he is a wonderful person.

28:27.040 --> 28:28.880
Although some bad things

28:29.440 --> 28:32.720
had happened in the past,

28:33.320 --> 28:35.480
he never gave up on himself.

28:36.440 --> 28:37.720
Instead, he worked hard

28:38.520 --> 28:40.360
and endured everything

28:41.800 --> 28:43.800
with a lot of hardship.

28:48.040 --> 28:49.000
If only

28:49.080 --> 28:51.360
you could see how excellent he is now.

28:51.440 --> 28:53.640
I'm sure you would have some regrets

28:54.200 --> 28:56.200
and worries too, right?

28:58.040 --> 28:59.600
But don't worry.

29:00.920 --> 29:02.680
I'll take good care of him.

29:04.040 --> 29:05.640
I'll make it up to him.

29:07.200 --> 29:08.240
I'll make sure

29:09.120 --> 29:10.840
he is happy every day.

29:12.920 --> 29:14.560
So I'll also give you my promise.

29:17.040 --> 29:18.600
As long as I am here,

29:20.240 --> 29:22.760
I won't let anyone bully Duan Jiaxu again.

29:34.160 --> 29:36.240
He'll have his own family in the future.

29:39.400 --> 29:40.680
He has me

29:43.000 --> 29:44.520
and many others who love him.

29:46.920 --> 29:48.120
We all love you.

29:54.080 --> 29:55.000
So

29:57.080 --> 29:59.280
you will never be alone anymore.

30:01.280 --> 30:02.160
Okay?

30:06.480 --> 30:07.560
Don't cry.

30:07.640 --> 30:08.880
If you cry,

30:10.000 --> 30:12.640
your mom will think I'm bullying you.

30:13.320 --> 30:14.920
The smoke is stinging my eyes.

30:17.320 --> 30:18.200
You promised.

30:19.320 --> 30:21.000
You promised in front of my mom

30:21.080 --> 30:23.160
that you'll protect me.

30:23.240 --> 30:24.760
Yes, I'll protect you.

30:27.720 --> 30:28.920
Come here.

30:29.000 --> 30:30.320
Let me protect you for a bit.

30:41.760 --> 30:43.200
Hey.

30:47.160 --> 30:48.080
Come and get me.

31:00.600 --> 31:01.720
Come after me.

31:04.280 --> 31:05.160
I can even stand up.

31:07.320 --> 31:08.960
That little girl

31:09.040 --> 31:10.920
who used to sit in my back seat

31:11.880 --> 31:13.680
suddenly grew up one day.

31:14.600 --> 31:16.240
She can always accompany me

31:16.880 --> 31:18.360
and walk side by side with me.

31:19.840 --> 31:21.040
She helped me overcome

31:21.120 --> 31:23.080
my longest and darkest hour.

31:24.160 --> 31:25.720
She even took the lead

31:26.680 --> 31:28.040
and waited for me

31:29.040 --> 31:30.160
in the sunlight.

31:37.160 --> 31:38.040
Come on!

31:39.120 --> 31:39.960
I'm coming!

32:15.920 --> 32:18.680
I've submitted my resignation to Siyun.

32:22.280 --> 32:23.400
Why?

32:26.520 --> 32:28.440
Didn't I tell you before?

32:28.520 --> 32:30.080
You don't have to go back to Nanwu.

32:30.160 --> 32:31.760
I want to go back.

32:33.040 --> 32:33.960
I want

32:34.520 --> 32:36.160
to go in advance and get things settled.

32:37.040 --> 32:38.680
When you graduate and return to Nanwu,

32:38.760 --> 32:40.240
you can immediately start a good life.

32:41.080 --> 32:43.160
Besides, your family is there.

32:43.240 --> 32:44.960
I can start my business anywhere, right?

32:45.520 --> 32:48.680
My home is where you are.

32:52.440 --> 32:53.480
Didn't you say

32:54.120 --> 32:56.200
that after all the bad things are over,

32:56.680 --> 32:59.360
all that is left are the good things?

33:01.200 --> 33:03.080
So we just need to focus on the future.

33:04.280 --> 33:05.760
Our future.

33:07.440 --> 33:08.280
Okay?

33:13.440 --> 33:14.800
How long will it be before leaving?

33:16.880 --> 33:19.040
After completing the handover procedures,

33:19.880 --> 33:20.760
about a month later.

33:22.440 --> 33:23.440
A month?

33:27.000 --> 33:27.920
That's so soon.

33:31.400 --> 33:32.480
Are you feeling reluctant?

33:34.720 --> 33:35.640
No.

33:38.640 --> 33:40.160
But I feel reluctant.

33:49.840 --> 33:50.840
Don't worry.

33:50.920 --> 33:52.600
We'll have many opportunities to meet up.

34:09.639 --> 34:11.320
I'm making supper for you.

34:12.040 --> 34:13.239
Supper?

34:13.320 --> 34:14.639
Glutinous rice balls.

34:15.800 --> 34:17.199
How about six?

34:17.920 --> 34:18.800
Is that okay?

34:53.239 --> 34:54.199
Okay, that's enough.

34:56.159 --> 34:57.680
That's too much water.

34:58.200 --> 34:59.200
Really?

34:59.280 --> 35:00.160
Let me do it.

35:05.880 --> 35:06.760
That's about it.

35:22.120 --> 35:23.800
I'm going to miss you after I leave.

35:23.880 --> 35:24.840
What am I going to do?

35:32.160 --> 35:34.920
If you miss me,

35:36.240 --> 35:37.840
you can eat the candy I gave you.

35:37.920 --> 35:39.120
Okay?

35:39.680 --> 35:41.400
Or you can bring the polar bear with you.

35:43.680 --> 35:45.520
What will you do if you miss me?

35:49.920 --> 35:51.320
I'll leave the polar bear with you.

35:53.000 --> 35:54.560
If you miss me,

35:54.640 --> 35:55.800
you can look at it.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.640
It will be just like I'm right beside you.

35:58.240 --> 35:59.080
Okay?

36:04.440 --> 36:05.560
It's not done yet.

36:14.360 --> 36:15.320
Do you want…

36:22.440 --> 36:23.640
What are you thinking about?

36:23.720 --> 36:25.640
Why don't you go and get some rest?

36:25.720 --> 36:26.840
I'll be done soon.

36:32.320 --> 36:33.200
How about…

37:27.200 --> 37:28.120
All right.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.240
I've called a car for you.

37:30.320 --> 37:32.960
Text me after you get in the car.

37:35.440 --> 37:36.600
The airport is so far.

37:37.280 --> 37:38.720
I shouldn't have let you see me off.

37:40.040 --> 37:42.000
How could I not come to see you off?

37:48.400 --> 37:49.480
I don't want you to leave.

37:59.920 --> 38:00.760
I know.

38:02.760 --> 38:03.680
Don't worry.

38:04.920 --> 38:06.120
After I get there,

38:07.040 --> 38:08.520
I'll visit you whenever I have time.

38:09.200 --> 38:11.000
I won't make you wait too long. Okay?

38:14.920 --> 38:16.040
Listen.

38:17.560 --> 38:19.520
Once you're back in Nanwu,

38:20.520 --> 38:21.840
you need to eat regularly.

38:22.840 --> 38:23.760
You must have

38:24.720 --> 38:26.560
three meals a day.

38:26.640 --> 38:27.840
But I'll remind you.

38:28.920 --> 38:29.960
And also,

38:31.200 --> 38:32.280
don't think

38:33.000 --> 38:34.160
about other things.

38:34.240 --> 38:35.400
Don't be concerned about them.

38:36.240 --> 38:37.560
Just focus on your work

38:37.640 --> 38:39.200
and work hard.

38:39.280 --> 38:40.600
You can work hard,

38:41.120 --> 38:42.680
but don't stress yourself too much.

38:43.640 --> 38:44.480
I mean,

38:45.360 --> 38:47.800
if your start-up does fail,

38:47.880 --> 38:49.040
it's okay.

38:49.720 --> 38:51.840
After all, I can…

38:53.640 --> 38:54.520
You can what?

38:56.240 --> 38:57.360
I'll provide for you.

39:00.000 --> 39:01.960
After I graduate, I can provide for you.

39:03.080 --> 39:04.520
You always say you'll provide for me.

39:05.320 --> 39:06.320
Then I'll just wait.

39:11.280 --> 39:12.160
All right.

39:12.680 --> 39:13.760
Well,

39:15.280 --> 39:16.560
I'm going to go now.

39:16.640 --> 39:17.720
Don't stay any longer.

39:18.880 --> 39:19.720
Okay?

39:23.160 --> 39:24.680
Text me after you get in the car.

39:26.440 --> 39:27.360
I'm going now.

39:37.720 --> 39:39.000
Be good.

39:41.200 --> 39:42.960
Text me when you get in the car.

39:43.040 --> 39:43.880
Head back now.

39:45.960 --> 39:47.000
Bye.

40:14.040 --> 40:15.480
Let me send you off.

40:22.320 --> 40:23.480
Okay.

40:24.480 --> 40:25.720
Then send me off.

40:45.440 --> 40:46.640
This is far enough.

40:48.520 --> 40:49.600
I really have to go now.

40:53.080 --> 40:54.240
Head back now.

40:54.320 --> 40:55.760
Text me when you get in the car.

40:58.200 --> 40:59.760
Make sure to text me.

41:40.600 --> 41:41.560
What is it?

41:42.920 --> 41:43.960
I have a feeling

41:44.720 --> 41:46.320
that you have something to tell me.

41:50.240 --> 41:51.760
After you go to Nanwu,

41:52.720 --> 41:54.800
can we have video calls every day?

41:55.360 --> 41:56.440
Of course we can.

41:57.400 --> 42:00.240
You won't find it burdensome, will you?

42:01.600 --> 42:02.680
Will you find it burdensome?

42:02.760 --> 42:04.720
- No.
- Me neither.

42:08.920 --> 42:09.840
You try it first.

42:12.480 --> 42:13.360
Okay.

42:25.600 --> 42:26.480
One more thing.

42:28.040 --> 42:30.600
We'll be in a long-distance relationship,

42:31.200 --> 42:32.120
so we should

42:32.800 --> 42:34.600
make an extra effort.

42:34.680 --> 42:38.720
For example, on anniversaries or holidays,

42:38.800 --> 42:40.080
I can visit you in Nanwu

42:40.160 --> 42:41.920
or you can visit me in Yihe.

42:42.000 --> 42:43.080
Of course.

42:43.640 --> 42:44.920
Then I shall go and visit you.

42:46.400 --> 42:47.960
Hold on. What do you mean by that?

42:48.040 --> 42:49.280
Are you saying

42:49.360 --> 42:50.800
that I usually don't make an effort?

42:51.600 --> 42:52.480
That's not it.

42:53.160 --> 42:54.560
So do you agree with it?

42:54.640 --> 42:55.800
Of course.

42:55.880 --> 42:56.720
Good.

43:05.440 --> 43:06.720
And also,

43:08.920 --> 43:10.280
if we have an argument…

43:10.760 --> 43:12.480
We won't argue.

43:13.440 --> 43:15.080
But if we do,

43:15.160 --> 43:16.840
we must make up on the same day.

43:17.640 --> 43:19.280
No silent treatment. No disappearing.

43:20.520 --> 43:22.360
- Got it?
- We make up on the same day we quarrel.

43:23.520 --> 43:24.480
Well said.

43:27.200 --> 43:28.440
Trust.

43:29.080 --> 43:31.160
We trust each other.

43:31.240 --> 43:32.160
Actually…

43:32.760 --> 43:33.800
If…

43:34.800 --> 43:36.960
- What are you reading?
- Wait. No.

43:38.520 --> 43:40.720
"Guide to maintaining
a long-distance relationship"?

43:41.440 --> 43:42.760
As you know,

43:42.840 --> 43:44.600
many problems come up

43:44.680 --> 43:46.800
in long-distance relationships.

43:46.880 --> 43:48.880
So I summarized them in advance

43:49.480 --> 43:52.520
and developed a guide.

43:53.480 --> 43:55.400
So you don't trust me

43:55.480 --> 43:56.560
and are worried about me.

43:57.760 --> 43:59.000
No.

44:00.800 --> 44:02.120
I'm pretty worried about you.

44:02.680 --> 44:04.120
I think your guide

44:04.200 --> 44:05.720
is done very well.

44:05.800 --> 44:07.080
You should strictly follow it

44:07.160 --> 44:08.000
in the future.

44:08.920 --> 44:09.840
Me?

44:11.440 --> 44:12.520
Quickly send me a copy.

44:15.600 --> 44:17.120
You can make your own.

44:18.000 --> 44:18.960
I'm serious.

44:19.040 --> 44:20.600
What you wrote is really good.

44:27.280 --> 44:28.200
Wait.

44:29.000 --> 44:31.040
"We can have arguments,

44:31.120 --> 44:33.200
but not in front of other people."

44:33.280 --> 44:34.720
Yes, because it's a matter

44:34.800 --> 44:36.200
of saving our face.

44:38.760 --> 44:40.560
"You don't have to reply
to messages instantly.

44:40.640 --> 44:42.200
But if you see them, you must reply."

44:42.280 --> 44:44.200
- That's right.
- If you see them, you must reply.

44:44.280 --> 44:47.320
Yes, you have to reply if you see it.
Got it?
